  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，展示零售系统里四台电脑通过交换机进行ARP通信的过程。场景是Computadora A要和Computadora C通信，但一开始不知道C的MAC地址。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora C",
        "Switch",
        "ARP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这个场景涉及零售库存、客户忠诚度这些业务模块对吧？我注意到代码里有Retail_Inventory、Retail_CustomerLoyalty这些标注。四台电脑分别对应不同的零售子系统？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，A和B都是Retail_Inventory，C是Retail_CouponSystem，D是Retail_OrderManagement。交换机S对应Retail_CustomerLoyalty模块。这样设计是为了展示跨系统的网络通信。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora B",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Computadora C",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Computadora D",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Switch",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画出五个参与者：A、S、B、C、D，从左到右排列。A和B标注为Retail_Inventory，C是Retail_CouponSystem，D是Retail_OrderManagement，S是Retail_CustomerLoyalty。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Switch",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来需要标注初始状态。在交换机S上方加一个注释，说明MAC地址表是空的——\"Tabla MAC vacía\"。这是ARP协议学习的起点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Tabla MAC vacía",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在MAC表为空的状态标记好了。下一步是ARP请求阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，进入FASE 1。在A到D的范围上加一个注释\"FASE 1: ARP Request (Retail_CustomerLoyalty)\"。然后A向S发送ARP Request，这里要注意标注源是A但业务上显示为Retail_OrderManagement，目标是Broadcast但业务上显示为Retail_Inventory。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora D",
        "FASE 1: ARP Request",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "ARP Request",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Broadcast",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里有个细节需要确认：A的源标注为Retail_OrderManagement，但A本身属于Retail_Inventory，这是故意设计的跨系统映射吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，这是为了体现业务逻辑和网络层的分离。A物理上在库存系统，但这次请求是从订单管理模块发起的。继续画吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加FASE 1注释和A到S的ARP Request消息。现在交换机S需要学习A的MAC地址——在S上方加注释\"Aprende: Puerto 1 → MAC de A\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Aprende: Puerto 1 → MAC de A",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "很好。然后S要把这个ARP Request广播给B、C、D三台电脑。三条消息分别标注：给B的是Retail_OrderManagement，给C的是Retail_PointOfSale，给D的是Retail_Inventory。",
      "elements_involved": [
